claimInBridgeTransfer.t.sol
├── given recovery mode is off
│  ├── when caller is not the Mechanic
│  │  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
│  └── when caller is the Mechanic
│     ├── given the spoke snapshot recording the outbound transfer was not reported
│     │  └── it should revert with BridgeStateMismatch
│     └── given the spoke snapshot recording the outbound transfer was reported
│        ├── it should decrease the corresponding adapter's token balance by amount
│        ├── it should increase the machine's token balance by amount
│        └── it should emit an InBridgeTransferClaimed event
└── given recovery mode is on
   ├── when caller is not the Security Council
   │  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
   └── when caller is the Security Council
      ├── given the spoke snapshot recording the outbound transfer was not reported
      │  └── it should revert with BridgeStateMismatch
      └── given the spoke snapshot recording the outbound transfer was reported
         ├── it should decrease the corresponding adapter's token balance by amount
         ├── it should increase the machine's token balance by amount
         └── it should emit an InBridgeTransferClaimed event
